Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真高兴啊，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C3系统第11号电源线被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从C4转接过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力丧失20%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库C区探测到火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2气密门的内壁破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰内温度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库防火隔间无法关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手动关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在那附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7、8、9蓄水池破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注40的水进第10至15蓄水池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急排出所有的喷射燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷第2、第3 ECS杆损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来把那个粗暴的家伙\n给我赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你赢了，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，好像也不是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动SDM，120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告，启动后无法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，快点动手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会陪我到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算自我引爆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来当好朋友吧，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舱门？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，还剩60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附带一提，炸药有300公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,份量足以炸沉这艘船舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴萨狄那的主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从方位2-9-8接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好诱饵机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快准备再度潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高压空气尚未充填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离2500
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认鱼雷发射管口的开启声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说想跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除所有攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就等于是终于得到了\n期望已久的初次打击机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛却因太阳西下而告中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼雷没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跟丢了我方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴萨狄那，在距离1500处停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行舱门正在开启
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种暴风雨中\n打开飞行舱门根本是自杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann没有任何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令是从别处发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不用担心，一切都会很顺利)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的，不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得很难看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你像英雄那般\n帅气的将我一次击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死命挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起华丽又滑稽的走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只剩15秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认全舰的空气密闭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以关闭飞行舱门为优先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，Arbalest(强弩兵)呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么亲密地叫我\n 卡西姆、卡西姆的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骂狗屎家伙耶，大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我说了一些没大脑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的事还一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的觉得你很帅
