Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航，潜航，潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,53、54、55节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定
