Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann，剩下就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，千鸟小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理查德德．马德加斯中校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
