Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波布．莱利中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史裘瓦特．亚凯尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔．马卡兰上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深感光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉…
