Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，你去跟她说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟我一起来吗？千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会做奇怪的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危险吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说那个，这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的钓场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地里只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要搭往东京的班机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能在这里\n再待40多分钟而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我当初的作战目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是想带你来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却因为各种事而绕了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，钓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定30分钟就可以钓到大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就很难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是钓上超乎想象的大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是从恐怖的危险中逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分钟就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你在，我现在才能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就来试试\n你所说的这种好运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拉了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲷鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是鲸鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不能否定这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要把它钓回家去喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
